/**
 * All declared types have this type.
 * Note: Type has itself as Type.
 * Reason for being in eliot.compiler: type checking must refer to this type, but the surface
 * syntax (the `[]` type-namespace marker, generic-parameter kinds) covers every ordinary use,
 * so it lives in the importable compiler package rather than the auto-imported prelude. The
 * resolver maps the bare name `Type` to this definition directly.
 */
type Type
